# Free Multiplayer mods for Forge 1.21.1

These mods allow for free multiplayer without the cost or hassle of setting up a server.


| Name | Links | Description | Alternatives |
|------|-------|-------------| --------------|
| E4MC | [CF](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/e4mc) / [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/e4mc) | Open a LAN server to anyone, anywhere, anytime. | - |
| Tunnely | [MR](https://modrinth.com/mod/tunnely) | Tunnely is a simple Minecraft mod that tunnels your local host server to the internet, letting friends join easily. | - |

\* - A must-have mod for nearly any modpack. Only in very rare circumstances should you not use this mod or an equivalent.

** - Prone to issues or conflicts with other mods